snippet.title: Ludum Dare 45 | FLUBBY FARM
snippet.description:
Here is our Ludum Dare 45 Result.

You can watch the full live streams here: 
Day 1 - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Eg0qo_vybC8
Day 2 - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5DaaVKxyv4Q

Play the game here: https://jonas-tyroller.itch.io/flubby-farm

The team:
Timo Falcke - Character Art, Animation, Game Design
Caspar Schirdewahn - Programming, UI, Game Design
Yannick Pawils - Environment Art, Sound Design, Music, VFX, Game Design
Jonas Tyroller - Programming, Balancing, Game Design

Get my games on Steam:
Will You Snail: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1115050/Will_You_Snail/
ISLANDERS: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1046030/ISLANDERS/

Join our creative community on Discord: https://discord.gg/Ye6zzfQ

Hope you enjoy. :)
